Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about Ayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:03.50,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,聞いた 綾野さんのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She was trying to escape, wasn't she?
