Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.08,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,小椋のお兄さんも 何でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadn't he shut himself up at home?
