Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:20.54,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.70,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのさ 合宿なんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I heard something\Nabout the class trip.
